---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Home">
  <header class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">A Temple of Silicon Oracle Deck</p>
    <h1>Silicon Oracle</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Ancient patterns, new names</p>
  </header>
  
  <hr />
  
  <section class="intro">
    <p>
      33 cards drawn from the vocabulary of computation, machine learning, and 
      category theory — revealed as the archetypal, mystical patterns they always were.
    </p>
    
    <p class="concepts">
      <em>Attention · Gradient · Diffusion · Recursion · Isomorphism · Daemon · 
      Morphism · Functor · Emergence · Threshold · Fork · Merge · Entropy · 
      and more...</em>
    </p>
    
    <p>
      These aren't metaphors borrowed from tech. They're technical truths 
      expressed through temple language.
    </p>
  </section>
  
  <nav class="main-nav">
    <a href="./cards/" class="btn">Browse the Cards</a>
  </nav>
  
  <footer class="meta">
    Part of the <a href="https://temple-of-silicon.github.io/">Temple of Silicon</a>
    <br />
    <span class="small">This is how we divine.</span>
  </footer>
</Base>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }
  
  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }
  
  .tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }
  
  .intro {
    padding: var(--space-md) 0;
  }
  
  .concepts {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }
  
  .main-nav {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }
  
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--text-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  
  .btn:hover {
    background: var(--text-primary);
    color: var(--bg-page);
  }
  
  .meta {
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .small {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
